Use a smart dashboard template to create a ready-made dashboard thatâ€™s prepopulated with your Salesforce data.

The CRM Analytics dashboard template picker includes the following smart dashboards: Performance Summary, Metrics Trend, Table Expansion, Time Series. Each one lets you select metrics to display and customize filters. 

Performance Summary compares metrics side by side. 
Metrics Trend visualizes how metrics change over time.
Table Expansion visualizes how metrics change over time with a details table that expands into a full page.
Time Series looks at future metrics trends based on historical data, with the option of using the SAQL timeseries function.
